    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.08)))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = wp.cos(0.14)
    tmp = ((0.21 - wp.abs(tmp + 0.57)) - (0.93 / 0.71))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.88) + ((v2 + 0.57 * v0 + 0.98) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.49)))
    v1 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.91 / v1 + 0.35) / 0.44))
    v0 = wp.cos(0.54)
    data[tid] = v0
